'''Chaos druids''' are low-level [[human]]s commonly killed for their frequent drops of [[herb]]s. Unlike most [[druid]]s, they worship both [[Guthix]] and [[Zamorak]]. They attack with their fists and make use of a spell that appears to be a combination of the [[Confuse]] and [[Bind]] spells, binding their target very briefly if successful.

Players who decide to kill Chaos Druids in Edgeville Dungeon should beware of player killers who disguise themselves in [[Zamorak monk robes|Zamorak robes]] to take on the appearance of a Chaos Druid. If you attack another player you will become [[skulled]] and potentially lose all of your items.

